OL,3,CBy-election date proposed in Guernsey
OL,4,Cafter Le Tocq's resignation
OL,6,FDeputy Sarah Hansmann Rouxel,
OL,7,FPresident of SACC, says: "This will be
OL,8,Fthe first by-election to take place
OL,9,Funder the island-wide voting system.
OL,11,F"Our Committee has sought to develop
OL,12,Fproposals for the by-election that are
OL,13,Fefficient, proportionately and keep
OL,14,Fcosts to a minimum while ensuring a
OL,15,Ffair process for candidates.
OL,17,F"Candidates will of course be free to
OL,18,Fproduce some printed copies of their
OL,19,Fmanifesto to make available to any
OL,20,Fvoters expressing a preference for a
OL,21,Fprinted copy."
